{"tid":940413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"神作《蓋世豪俠》將緊接《義不容情》播出！！！！！！","createTime":"2018-12-14T02:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T01:23:34.000Z","uid":224375,"like":7,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3994f937f5a8c90b225a0ee367c66dd9aa66ddb9","tid":940413,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1月1日播"},{"pid":"a8a13d314b291c42e907b8605eb29c350524ce20","tid":940413,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:20:29.000Z","msg":"資料來源：「威哥會館」<br />\n<br />\n大家準備今晚看第32集《義不容情》的同時，TVB已決定2019年1月1日重播1989年另一經典戲寶《蓋世豪俠》！《蓋世豪俠》其實與《義不容情》是TVB1989年4、5月同時播出的雙線劇，《義不容情》是7點35分時段，《蓋世豪俠》是9點05分時段，當時的確是「港劇盛世」！也是《蓋世豪俠》的出現，令周星馳這名字由1989年紅到2019年！<br />\n<br />\n周星馳的電影年青一輩也「睇到識背」，但其實電影內容很多對白與橋段也是由電視劇《蓋世豪俠》、《他來自江湖》、《孖仔孖心肝》中演變出來，所以如果未看過《蓋世豪俠》又不想買DVD的年青「星」迷，的確要重溫一下！<br />\n<br />\n而《義不容情》在2018年12月31日大除夕，更會連環播出49、50集，大家《義不容情》劇迷要多加留意！<br />\n<br />\n#蓋世豪俠 #周星馳 #羅慧娟 #吳孟達 #藍潔瑛 #吳鎮宇 #劉江 #梅小惠 #李麗麗 #艾威 #杜麗莎 #許紹雄 #高雄 #鮑方 #陳安瑩 #飲杯茶食個包 #不死極樂神功 #段古武辛府 #段飛 #李珠 #雪雁 #段玉樓 #古峰 #古艷陽"},{"pid":"8826ed2c30e238f74401d23e96baf62a1e1bff33","tid":940413,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"飲啖茶食個包<br />\n斷古母申府"},{"pid":"bb7389dcc5f5225356a3ba4e723444d60806815f","tid":940413,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8826ed2c30e238f74401d23e96baf62a1e1bff33","tid":940413,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:36:41.000Z","msg":"飲啖茶食個包<br />\n斷古母申府"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"段古武辛府 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"172812614fd0f09757bb2ca14e5b0afc260885f7","tid":940413,"uid":224375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:42:09.000Z","msg":"但𥚃面有幾個女角已經過左身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae501532d213b41a721e1dca910effab93c4ec0","tid":940413,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"其實最好播我本善良, 食住上, 可惜年頭播左"},{"pid":"2593e4e1f06bcde4a681c2625da6235e2daa1268","tid":940413,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ae501532d213b41a721e1dca910effab93c4ec0","tid":940413,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"其實最好播我本善良, 食住上, 可惜年頭播左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:31:21.000Z","msg":"我想佢播今生無悔"},{"pid":"75ccb8047b0c839fae004ebaf08172b0a85b7a0f","tid":940413,"uid":42848,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"又播<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n播得黃日華韋家輝不如順手播埋馬場大亨"},{"pid":"c9f87e572ac69881a72e7165ef33d33a61bd2ca9","tid":940413,"uid":89533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2593e4e1f06bcde4a681c2625da6235e2daa1268","tid":940413,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ae501532d213b41a721e1dca910effab93c4ec0","tid":940413,"uid":198841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"其實最好播我本善良, 食住上, 可惜年頭播左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:31:21.000Z","msg":"我想佢播今生無悔"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"黎明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58cc412afc7fad2030990695e3842d4850def9bb","tid":940413,"uid":144735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75ccb8047b0c839fae004ebaf08172b0a85b7a0f","tid":940413,"uid":42848,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"c